<ul>
  <li>Create a directory called <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Lab5</code> and change your current working directory to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Lab5</code>. You will complete the entire lab from this directory.</li>
  <li>Before you start working on this lab, prepare your submission file and make an initial commit.</li>
